{
  "version": "3.0.1",
  "releaseNotes": {
    "zh": [
      "修复 macOS 应用内更新下载完成后无法准备和打开 DMG 的问题。",
      "分页图片与长图阅读器恢复双指缩放，并避免缩放时误翻页。",
      "优化图片、EPUB 和 DOCX 阅读器的后台解析与返回动画，快速返回更加流畅。",
      "智能调整顺序升级为按页面和栏位最佳填充，短词条会补入当前页剩余空间。",
      "设置中新增低开销开发者模式，可导出或删除包含完整错误堆栈的详细诊断日志。",
      "Android 设置标题旁新增当前版本号。"
    ],
    "en": [
      "Fixed macOS in-app updates failing to prepare and open the DMG after download.",
      "Restored pinch zoom for page images and long images without accidental page changes.",
      "Moved reader parsing off the UI thread and shortened reverse transitions for smooth quick returns.",
      "Upgraded Smart reorder with page-and-column best-fit packing.",
      "Added an opt-in low-overhead Developer mode with full diagnostic log export and deletion.",
      "Added the installed version beside the Android Settings title."
    ]
  },
